
### 2. `linux/debian/fail2ban/jail.local`

```ini
# =====================================================
# Rank 3: Fail2Ban SSH Jail Configuration
# Defensive Hardening Portfolio - Debian 13
# =====================================================

[sshd]
enabled = true
port = 50022
backend = systemd
filter = sshd
maxretry = 4
findtime = 10m
bantime = 86400        # Ban for 24 hours
ignoreip = 127.0.0.1 ::1 192.168.0.0/24   # Whitelist local network
